<h4>Leverage vacant public land for housing</h4>
<ul>
<li>Expedite the development of affordable housing on vacant, publicly-owned land</li>
<li>Expedite the development of blighted, vacant, delinquent
, and distressed properties</li></ul>

<h4> Create and expand housing affordability tools</h4>
<ul>
<li>Expand local homeownership via down payment assistance programs</li>
<li>Expand the joint use of 4% Low Income Housing Tax Credits with Tax Exempt Bonds</li>
<li>Preserve housing through the Rental Assistance Demonstration program</li>
<li>Support the ability to secure additional resources through the New Markets Tax Credits program</li></ul>

<h4>Enhance community engagement</h4>
<ul>
<li>Implement innovative techniques to support community engagement</li></ul>
